Package com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor.mp3

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Mp3Extractor.Seeker
    SeekMap that also allows mapping from position (byte offset) back to time, which can be used to work out the new sample basis timestamp after seeking and resynchronization.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstantBitrateSeeker
    MP3 seeker that doesn't rely on metadata and seeks assuming the source has a constant bitrate.
    Mp3Extractor
    Extracts data from the MP3 container format.
    Mp3ExtractorTest
    Unit test for Mp3Extractor.
    VbriSeeker
    MP3 seeker that uses metadata from a VBRI header.
    XingSeeker
    MP3 seeker that uses metadata from a Xing header.
    XingSeekerTest
    Tests for XingSeeker.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Mp3Extractor.Flags
    Flags controlling the behavior of the extractor.
